    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-01-25T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-01-25T00:00:00-05:00" n="1" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1">
                <head>No. 1.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Seat</persName> to
                            Mr. <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bluefields,
                                    Nicaragua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-01-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 25,
                            1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Honduras invading at Cape Gracias. Lives and millions property American
                        citizens unprotected. Appeal for man-of-war to Blueflelds Mosquito
                        Reservation, at once.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Seat</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Consular
                                Agent</hi>
                    </signed>,<lb/>(and fifty citizens of the United
                        States).</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
